N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 20 ยง 64.1 - Reports by licensees upon request

State Regulations

All persons who are not distributors but who have a
wholesale or retail license issued by the State Liquor Authority must, if
requested to do so, file with the Commissioner of Taxation and Finance reports
on forms furnished by such commissioner. Notes
